data.description: Beautiful, well maintained Townhouse in Village North. This three bedroom 2 and half bath features a pleasent color palete, valuted ceilings, wood burning fireplace. New roof, new windows, new doors, new stainless steel appliances, new garage door. French doors leading to a tastefully redone enclose porch for addtional entertainment space.  Close to shopping, downtown entertainment and dining. Short drive to the World Equestrian Center. Low HOA includes water, lawn maintance, pool and common areas.
